description:
Mysti Mayhem is an unsigned indie artist and has been performing for the last decade across the United States and Europe. After graduating high school, she moved from Pennsylvania to Florida where she met her first mentor, Bo Diddley, and learned how to transition her powerhouse vocals from an operatic background to a blues platform. 

From there she joined forces with Spellbox, an acoustic duo based out of Gainesville, FL. Her travels across the United States and multiple independent recordings led to a $50K fan funded album with Sellaband in 2006. Mysti Mayhem's most recent release, also a fan funded album, is her 6th to date. She currently resides in North Carolina performing and in constant search of new musical opportunities and endeavors.


- Personally, I think she is wonderful. She has a lovely voice.
